{
  "stem": "1491.2",
  "chunk_idx": 8,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 7.5,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 61,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And because they said the Russians start the war against Germany, and we thought the war will be over any day.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 61,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "But in meanwhile, we didn't see any end to it.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 61,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And always, we heard the Russians are getting closer, and the Germans trying to cover their-- what you call this, how to say it-- to cover their-- to cover what they did to us.",
      "word_count": 34
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 62,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Digging up graves, burning the bodies, which was part of my work.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 62,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And the smell-- you can't imagine what the awful smell.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 63,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "When back in Plaszow.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 63,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "They tried to cover up and to cover the graves.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 63,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "There shouldn't be any marks left of what they did to Jewish people.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 64,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I went because the Russians were getting closer.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 64,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And Schindler had to liquidate this camp.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 65,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "1944.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 66,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "In the summer.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 66,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I would say September, July, I don't know.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 66,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "But he had to liquidate Emalia.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 66,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And he built a new camp in Czechoslovakia, called Brnenec, for his people, the ammunition factory.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 67,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "We went to Plaszow to wait for the transport.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 67,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "We were supposed to go from Plaszow straight to Brnenec.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 67,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "What happened in between, I really don't know.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 67,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "But we were in Plaszow for a nice few months.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 68,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "We were petrified.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 68,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "We were petrified, because, still, a few people remained in Emalia for the liquidation of the camp.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 68,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And my father didn't know what to do, if we should go with the transport to Plaszow, which was hell on earth, or to be left to the liquidation of camp.",
      "word_count": 31
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 68,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "But usually, when they were liquidating camps, they liquidate the people.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 68,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "So this was our choice, to go back to Plaszow.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 68,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "We had no other choice.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 69,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "A thousand people.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 70,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Most of them.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 70,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "We were 300 women, 700 men.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 70,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "So most of them went back to Plaszow.",
      "word_count": 8
    }
  ],
